Toads Wild Adventure Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 2026
Toads Wild Adventure is a family-friendly puzzle and arcade game. Your privacy is important.
Information We Collect
Toads Wild Adventure does not collect personal information.
The app does not require:
an account
a login
an email address
a subscription
an in-app purchase
location access
camera access
microphone access
contacts access
Data Collection
Toads Wild Adventure does not collect, store, sell, share, or transmit personal data.
The app does not use third-party advertising or analytics services.
Internet Connection
Toads Wild Adventure does not require an internet connection for normal gameplay.
Children’s Privacy
Toads Wild Adventure is designed to be family-friendly. The app does not knowingly collect personal information from children or any other users.
In-Game Progress
The app may save basic gameplay progress locally on your device, such as settings, stars, streaks, or game progress. This information stays on your device and is not sent to the developer or any third party.
Ads and Purchases
Toads Wild Adventure does not include ads.
Toads Wild Adventure does not include in-app purchases.
Contact
